verses.1: Israel-te, Egypt gam panin pusuakin, Jakob innkuanpihte pau dang a zang mite kiang pan a paikhiat uh ciangin
verses.2: Judah-te, Topa始 mi siangtho suak a, Israel-te, ama uk mi a suak hi.
verses.3: Tuipi in amaute mu-in tai khia a, Jordan gun a nungkik hi.
verses.4: Mual liante tuutal bangin diang uh a, mual neute tuuno bangin a diang uh hi.
verses.5: Tuipi aw, na taikhiat nading, Jordan gun aw, na nungkik nading,
verses.6: mual liante aw, tuu bangin mual neute aw, tuuno bangin na dianna ding uh bang in hong nasak ahi hiam?
verses.7: Leitung aw, suangpi, bualtui suaksak a, meisuang, ciktui a suaksak, Jakob始 Pasian始 omna, Topa始 omna ah liing in.
